---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "@/components/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  SEOTitle="Geospatial Intelligence | PrincipalAI"
  SEODescription="AI-assisted spatial intelligence, mapping, accessibility analysis, and location-based decision support."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#071f3f] via-[#123f86] to-[#e8f4ff] px-8 py-24 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-100">
        Geospatial Intelligence
      </p>
      <h1 class="max-w-5xl font-serif text-5xl font-bold leading-tight sm:text-6xl">
        Spatial intelligence for place-based decisions.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
        PrincipalAI helps organisations combine spatial data, models, maps, and AI-assisted interpretation to understand where risks, opportunities, and impacts occur.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
        Request a demonstration
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            The problem
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Many decisions depend on where impacts occur.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Policy, infrastructure, health, climate, transport, and investment decisions often vary sharply across places. National averages can hide local risks, access constraints, equity issues, and spatial trade-offs.
          </p>
          <p>
            Geospatial Intelligence provides a decision-support layer that helps users interrogate spatial evidence, compare locations, and generate clearer insight from maps, indicators, and location-based models.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
          What it supports
        </p>
        <h2 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          AI-assisted spatial analysis for operational and strategic decisions.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Local impact analysis</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Identify where impacts, risks, and opportunities are concentrated across places and communities.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Accessibility intelligence</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Assess access to services, jobs, infrastructure, health care, transport, and other critical opportunities.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Spatial comparison</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Compare regions, communities, corridors, catchments, or service areas using consistent spatial evidence.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Map-based reporting</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Generate structured summaries that explain spatial patterns, drivers, and decision implications.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Example applications
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Designed for decisions that vary by place.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Which communities have the weakest access to critical services?
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Where are infrastructure risks, climate exposure, and population vulnerability concentrated?
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Which locations would benefit most from a proposed investment or intervention?
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            How do local impacts differ across demographic, economic, or service-access groups?
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Why PrincipalAI
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Spatial intelligence connected to economics, modelling, and policy.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            PrincipalAI’s geospatial capability is designed for applied decision-making, not mapping alone. It connects spatial evidence with economic, social, infrastructure, and environmental analysis.
          </p>
          <p>
            We help organisations move from maps and indicators to clearer interpretation, option assessment, and decision support.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#071f3f] px-8 py-20 text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Turn spatial evidence into place-based decisions.
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
          Talk to PrincipalAI about geospatial intelligence, accessibility analysis, spatial dashboards, and location-based decision support.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
          Request a demonstration
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
